Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是沒辦法吧  塔斯克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不成器的依古西奧拉可發揮不了用處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來撫養這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克你？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撫養這個不成器的依古西奧拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因為他不成器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洗澡太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音太大啦  鄰居都能聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是已經忘記  對潛入記憶拯救你的我感恩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是那  這歸這
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  剛才偷看我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒看沒看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天有採訪的工作  拜託你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,採訪者是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有田紫苑小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近你的活躍已經備受矚目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請問感想如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你問我感想…的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  有沒有想過當演員？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎很適合演動作電影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,動作…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我調查了你的戶籍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相當複雜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,曾祖母是居住在夏威夷的美國人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與從日本移居而來的曾祖父結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的長女在俄羅斯結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她的獨生子回到日本後與日本女性結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雙親現在居住在莫斯科
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我的日語有點奇怪的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這世道戶籍什麼的找個黑客就能隨便偽造出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  我不是很明白的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自從知道你後一直有奇怪的事件發生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的東京灣怪光事件也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你用拳頭擊毀大樓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有如同在空中飛行般的跳躍我都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,室戶先生您是不是醉了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是很認真的問題  而且我還沒有寫成新聞的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以希望你能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你之前參加了神明書房的葬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你和老闆是什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是宇宙聯邦的搜查官  為了追捕兇惡的罪犯來到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊作為偶像活動  一邊日夜工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀哈☆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣你滿意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把我當白癡啊  那個女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可憐  一個人很不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以後在叔叔家裡安心生活就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山海環抱  是個很悠閒的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最小的孩子很期待能有個姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搬家的準備就全交給叔叔好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼都不用操心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  神明醫生在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生的話  在那邊有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點哦  你還是那麼笨手笨腳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊  把空罐扔在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  室戶先生怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在不斷打探著我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不是什麼壞人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定也會到你這邊來問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  我會適當地糊弄過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了！神明先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你與有田小姐幸福！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她到哪裡去了？  你想想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在周圍找她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼討厭到親戚家裡去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:06:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她都說「祝你與有田小姐幸福」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像產生了奇怪的誤會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說  不是誤會的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然房間裡沒人  但曾今回來過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她大概會去什麼地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她還是個孩子  應該不會跑太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拄拐杖的女孩？  說起來是來過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在ATM機取了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道去了哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來是向車站去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虧你能注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我在地球住得比你長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}列車即將到站
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}為了您的安全  請退到白線內側
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該去哪裡呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失戀的女孩果然應該向北嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈多流
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那女人也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子  你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴…巴迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別叫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  你在做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人好野蠻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你！竟然對這麼小的孩子下手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫警察比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誤…誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了  竟然耍那種手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個  你不能這麼張揚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飛越站台  被人拍到的話會引起騷亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比如室戶先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆別異口同聲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你看  已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  絕對抓不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於要開始發佈CD了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可一定得買啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要買的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盯上我們的果然不是那個聯邦搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那個依古西奧拉的聯邦搜查官的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有誰能做到那種殺人方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有超強的體力是做不到那種殺人方式的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有那種力量的就只有依古西奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼一定要被那樣殘忍的方式殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個搜查官為什麼那麼恨我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的話  應該沒有用這種費事的殺人方式的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那其他還能是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  還有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一個依古西奧拉在這個行星？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  以前略有耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼可笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只是回想起了以前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人看到像翔子的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接著我一層一層地下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她要是在這大樓裡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會走那麼遠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是  走路不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是一個原因  但是那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}現在播報尋人啟示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}有田紫苑小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}有田紫苑小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}各務翔子小姐在6層電梯前等你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}有田紫苑小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的小紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的廣播不是騙人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  有田紫苑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寫真偶像的紫苑在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,採購完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you  幫了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到紫苑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請給我簽名！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鬧什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有藝人來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請表演一下「安」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我買了CD
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請與我合影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,活該  笨偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有田紫苑真的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到郵件了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那還不快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敢算計我  膽子不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對方是小孩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  有人找茬就得反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同等級啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出了點麻煩  說起來翔子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後再聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,插隊可不好啊  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,追上前面的計程車
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？  事出有因的話就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,司機  甩掉後面的計程車
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在被壞人追趕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  該我展示身手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是難纏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個司機  技術不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個司機  可不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我自己跑更快的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被擺了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼  是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥也轉這行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,車費！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先繞到站點去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  翔子會不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  接下來去哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我該去哪裡呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到終點了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,腳似乎不方便呢  我背你下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子是國中一年級啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望那個人來接你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼呢  快放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭奈多流  你和有田紫苑摟摟抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩人相抱的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是在醫院的走廊裡相抱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那是她快摔倒了  所以扶她一把而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  別這麼快下定論啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  回醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔也很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不想去叔叔家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟奈多流分開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不可能一直和翔子在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,親戚的叔叔很和藹啊  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有田小姐也快來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是之前來避難所取材的那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有田的熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧  我叫千川功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她很喜歡那塔魯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像兄妹關係一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從小時候就認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  翔子的哥哥是怎樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是個不錯的傢伙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外表上看不出來  他做菜很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然在意外中失去了雙親  但他總是很開朗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也很重視翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很溫柔的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還兩人一起逃課
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  第一次見到各務的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學校的池子發出很響的聲音  然後我們就逃課去看了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他還活著的話  也想讓巴迪你見見的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們一定合得來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡治療腿的同時慢慢考慮要不要來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉呢  沒有考慮到翔子的感受就擅做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢  不要討厭叔叔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子那邊很順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她本來就是很開朗的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會得到疼愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯  你其實很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別捉弄我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  又會摔倒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身為依古西奧拉卻這麼笨手笨腳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯  你比我個子高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神明書房的兒子和有田紫苑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神明先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下週起可回收垃圾的回收日改為星期一了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要弄錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不可燃垃圾是星期二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可燃垃圾是星期三和星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都像神明先生那樣認真就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在房間埋伏的莫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.00,0:23:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被槍擊中的那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但在意識模糊之際  新的力量發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那份力量是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後巴迪接到了那塔魯的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他的言語中能夠感受到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯  你究竟想做什麼？
